OL,3,CMan in his 80s dies after being struck
OL,4,Cby HGV on A1
OL,6,FAn elderly man has died after being
OL,7,Fstruck by an HGV on the A1 in
OL,8,FGateshead.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a report of a
OL,11,Fcollision involving a pedestrian and a
OL,12,FScania HGV on the southbound
OL,13,Fcarriageway, shortly after the
OL,14,FMetrocentre junction towards Dunston,
OL,15,Fat 10.15am on Monday (25 November).
OL,17,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,18,Fwhere the pedestrian, a man in his
OL,19,F80s, died at the scene.
