OL,3,CMan in his 80s dies after being struck
OL,4,Cby HGV on A1
OL,6,FIt is believed he was linked to a
OL,7,Fwhite Ford Edge car parked nearby.
OL,9,FThe man's next of kin have been
OL,10,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,11,Fspecially-trained officers.
OL,13,FThe driver of the heavy goods vehicle
OL,14,Fremained at the scene, and is
OL,15,Fassisting officers with their
OL,16,Fenquiries.
OL,18,FA section of the road was closed in
OL,19,Fboth directions for around four hours,
OL,20,Fbut has since been re-opened.
