OL,3,CMan in his 80s dies after being struck
OL,4,Cby HGV on A1
OL,6,FPolice are now appealing for
OL,7,Finformation and witnesses to come
OL,8,Fforward.
OL,10,FSergeant Dave Roberts, of Northumbria
OL,11,FPolice, said: "Firstly, our thoughts
OL,12,Fgo out to the man's family and loved
OL,13,Fones at this tragic time.
OL,15,F"A range of enquiries are underway as
OL,16,Fwe try to establish exactly what has
OL,17,Fhappened in the moments leading up to
OL,18,Fthe collision.
