OL,6,F"As part of this, we are keen to hear
OL,7,Ffrom any motorists who were driving in
OL,8,Fthe area at the time, and any other
OL,9,Fwitnesses who may have saw what
OL,10,Fhappened."
OL,12,FHe continued: "We know this is a busy
OL,13,Fsection of the A1, and the collision
OL,14,Fhappened while there were lots of
OL,15,Fother vehicles on both sides of the
OL,16,Froad.
OL,18,F"We're especially keen to hear from
OL,19,Fanyone who may have dashcam footage,
OL,20,Fand those who saw the Ford Edge or
OL,21,FScania vehicles travelling in the area.
